* Also, We don't have NFC
---
 .../boot/dts/qcom/ulysse-common/common-disable.dtsi  | 12 ++++++++++++
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/ulysse-common/common.dtsi   |  2 ++
 2 files changed, 14 insertions(+)
